OL,3,CBosses drop threat of job losses at
OL,4,CScunthorpe steelworks
OL,6,FThe new bosses of British Steel have
OL,7,Fdropped the threat of job losses in
OL,8,FScunthorpe after the government took
OL,9,Fcontrol of the town's plant.
OL,11,FBritish Steel's Chinese owners Jingye
OL,12,Fhad put up to 2,700 workers at risk of
OL,13,Fredundancy after announcing that they
OL,14,Fplanned to close Scunthorpe's two
OL,15,Fblast furnaces, saying they were no
OL,16,Flonger financially viable.
OL,18,FMinisters intervened to pass an
OL,19,Femergency law to take over the running
OL,20,Fof the company on Saturday, 12 April.
