OL,6,FRaw materials to keep the blast
OL,7,Ffurnaces operational arrived last week.
OL,9,FOn Tuesday British Steel's interim
OL,10,Fchief commercial officer Lisa Coulson
OL,11,Fthanked workers for their
OL,12,F"extraordinary dedication" as she
OL,13,Fconfirmed the redundancy consultation
OL,14,Fhad been called off.
OL,16,FShe said: "Since the government passed
OL,17,Fits legislation, we have been working
OL,18,Fday and night to ensure we are able to
OL,19,Fstabilise our operations.
