OL,4,CScunthorpe steelworks
OL,6,F"The work done to secure the raw
OL,7,Fmaterials we need for both Queen Anne
OL,8,Fand Queen Bess blast furnaces means we
OL,9,Fare able to run both continuously."
OL,11,FUnions have welcomed the news.
OL,13,FGMB national officer Charlotte
OL,14,FBrumpton-Childs said it was "fantastic
OL,15,Fnews for steel workers and the people
OL,16,Fof Scunthorpe".
OL,18,F"It's like a cloud has been lifted
OL,19,Ffrom above the whole community," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
